                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "*[Bug 18972] diff(x=<m-by-n>, l, d) drops dimensions when l*d >= m*\n"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "https:\/\/bugs.r-project.org\/show_bug.cgi?id=18972"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\n--- Comment #10 from Suharto Anggono ("
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "mailto:suharto_anggono@yahoo.com",
                                "text": "suharto_anggono@yahoo.com"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": ") ---\n(In reply to Suharto Anggono from comment #5)"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_quote",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Created attachment 3572\n No early return for lag * differences >= xlen"
                            }
                        ],
                        "contains_padding": true
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\nInstead of\n\n    r[if (lag < (len <- nrow(r))) -len:-(len - lag + 1) else integer(), , drop\n= FALSE]\n\nand\n\n    r[if (lag < (len <- length(r))) -len:-(len - lag + 1L) else integer()]\n\n, now I prefer\n\n    r[-nrow(r):-max(nrow(r) - lag + 1L, 1L), , drop = FALSE]\n\nand\n\n    r[-length(r):-max(length(r) - lag + 1L, 1L)]\n\n."
